院：</strong>ns.admissions@imperial.ac.uk or +44 (0)20 7594 7260*(16)</p><p><strong>转学申请</strong></p><p>国内本科大三或大四的学生可以转入帝国理工学院二年级，但实质非常罕见，因为帝国理工学院本身就极少接受转学生（大一申帝国理工并不认为是转学申请）。帝国理工大三（也即本科最后一年）不接受转学生。*(11)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>奖学金搜索工具：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlEhLa4bVGapPPPPPPVHnY3unby7VdihihR7cK7vi0PA8TW6a3WcajPmauWeFoyL5oneiAp3MhZpkBZesl2b34dh' target='_blank'>Scholarships search tool</a></li>	<li>本科录取政策：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhljDkbcX2zN0rmjRoi3a2csHpSf_DavNh5T13cHpwAgc2Rz1vNdJ5Q_DKbIWU5uPKSmRGu6emEEyWzfAR_DLjNhWLcYXE6_B-NrR5ZQA1E06Pn56grR6X_sKHYWU5ORzfQAEExfPPmOk1eaLm1E06zASo3KWT0rrSD_A8WLX9LF3h7U8' target='_blank'>UNDERGRADUATE ADMISSIONS POLICY</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>本科项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=0rRNYslRLuKMyWATfZ9ZUXrS747QeHCtpYlDhc4At9pCAN2brhdR8-VdUAqWyw1ZS7xSNEWknlEISOaWxzSVGwoXTe0CZIw9EFqc3JUhQsvwE9XEhdKnj' target='_blank'>Courses for 2016 entry</a></li></ul><p>参考资料</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhZ3L8zwPUI7yybLKiwX2MdNWnG-8gkMO9W8wNbKSOF9twudoa7K1FtDccq5HeUwsoljO3PiSv7QSuP28a73nLY4lMhHRWkg069rwz9E4tXLSguFIHY8uq4pAKPg9y-Ql6' target='_blank'>When to apply</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=crr9MjJnkkP-GMsdNNNNNNQZoVQmCVwq67Cn8B8MGy8sG1_fcKD3zBubQv8YVNZFJ71scfozqI8gELtrDcf1h6g86ldFyczfYWNrL3do4Caf25zotGvSZ' target='_blank'>Deadlines for on-time applications</a> UCAS</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=OrMxo-G1wcXfYTO0hhhhhhO1ZUdJfuiWcpcpnXKYW7h3p_3NWGKNoXKjEXzFm80C25zjlXzNp8h625zXl7RjE7D3Wn0km8e9LcIEA4npUqWd' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BD_wWuxTbO0hhhhhhoA5DMklcm1hAukuky6mqL3W_q1KRjJd4fJd9fuN5d6GhVgkovInhvoGL4xs0kDX5neqiBQ5bBW-wJqyZJoACZ90fGuqkaRI_' target='_blank'>2015-16 Tuition Fees Unde