>	<li>材料实验室（Materials Laboratory）</li>	<li>物理性质与分析实验室（Physical Properties &amp; Analytics Laboratory）</li>	<li>反应与催化实验室（Reaction &amp; Catalysis Laboratory）</li>	<li>系统实验室（Systems Laboratory）</li>	<li>转移与分离实验室（Transport and Separation Laboratory）*(12)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbyepwOBAjfIBwwwwwwEKteC3p_jNV0V0szdG6I83b8AGBzAmszaKsqp3OhQ2KnpdlPC-' target='_blank'>Courses for 2015&ndash;16</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BkoLzABI5qnGGGGGGjj2L3YrbBX2nY4Y4fhJDL54F-VFM4KmnLB5nOqb8XBt6rhEa3DLnTDPvYc2AIn1Mp4szjZs2nGNMzvmT-x1hJtPYx7onuqO' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4sjL5VUFGEeBBBBBRRpZMtTeh6yApAEAE7wQ2ASvz8Oz5tx61Clk1PpZi7LBMO9aETdDMVdR_l5G_nOPQVGJ0vfJSta6_-ahnbSJFQvSUMlK4psOcB5U' target='_blank'>Academic requirements - China</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23uSwHR2VfesccccccwMCaAX95RmscKUKUIbE0w3-_xA_alqEtsS0tlXbnxBFjrXU-bGk5AG3obxvpVM7D_VH2ysHY0FfHsRXKOb' target='_blank'>Requirements for Graduate Studies</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=6ri8veO-kSynchLJbbbbbxXpAAs6kVrtUBaBauO208iKkqKA0GOAFuOS5u4JaLjRW-4gMu4AkALipW-4r0BkhaQIhF8ig0LRtamAK0DS60uSAkLipW-I' target='_blank'>When to apply</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_2cw1hiqOBI11111T1jPX5lRsDIuzhNhNHuTm61Xr08o4CGiKWGiDW1cmEAg2KTvXkHDlkX2QouE386qQktgEOqXAOyVpQ_WwQUxNVMLuQB7PhvGldN' target='_blank'>2015-16 Tuition Fees</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHN7YwPxI1bUWXpSGA5FnTbVStzkBbhq4lM7zBlPHoVSWoBekmYlHKQBe5wOdSWqfiejOsVrS17nG9vuOFdDo_pAD-HzJLmLuBV7OnRQ6u0sMO3nl_pDU3OnRR6pxhBBbKD05udQht2q9a8x31CHRd516