lank'>奖学金</a>提供给非欧盟国际学生，具体奖学金及申请方法等请见研究生的申请说明*(8)(9)</li></ul><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>帝国理工学院系统工程与创新中心主要开设有以下三个研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>可持续城市系统（Sustainable Urban Systems）</li>	<li>数据系统（Data Systems）</li>	<li>核电站施工事态发展（Nuclear Power Plants - Developments in Construction）*(9)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUw0SL1wLXOKGk8k09XaydqvVvJe-S9OfXKrbh4nn9LJPdrBQ0mQ5actp8J7atGe-St0ZrkDJq122sLqC' target='_blank'>Courses for 2015&ndash;16</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRYjL5VUFp21bbbbbbgj20R8M7BnY4Y4fhJASvz8Oz5cVKiGcNi9oNRhYv1AMC-Bh5OBtEbscK-BO5g92MgLo3p8ZXb0V5pT63_o7MHk' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwjowLo4OG6MHHHHH775ARjDXMlLuzhNhNpZLlqbUTA9Ts4LhFi_6FEA5UjqVDuohfjE-DRETFqKci1_WNfA4Cpd4PinWn0km8e93IEwUi4Y-DhUDO1oi' target='_blank'>Academic requirements - China</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_1okEmsA3OcEEEEEEbh_T8SFaCoetetiAPXVWmS0mQXcAQRX2zGn2VsUI6AyQViW2VNhI7sOTtu7AnwpK8whJeRMfX2zD' target='_blank'>Requirements for Graduate Studies</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCWAckzD3-bOcEEEEEWsLpADnBaZTlDU9U9-_QfbXBlcmlhbf9jHTQjmJcwbAIqKrI8MSjHvSi9XWrcaVf9dcF7Zfp-ZtLcV4CnpAmYA4OE-bZIavZiwR64EBk6' target='_blank'>When to apply</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=0rRNYslRLuKMyLyXrrrrrJrnuah5mwnoeh-P-PDvl9F-clz6urNxz0DxzYDj5x-XrG3pkL-IJb-LkLDi_80at7ev9XjFiVjm9Tcdv_c5RJWjvN6dmaWJXn-P' target='_blank'>2015-16 Tuition Fees</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUw0eLPIma-4m99999DyNAPQWw3sgwKfMfMXAFm-_W0nH0mjPJR0isRppZi7LBMO9lpyL9K3LkF9i7wXkEDvERJgERbqOL2R7fC300sw0HqP3OTO7ZRIisRR