务方向（Energy Business pathway）</li>	<li>管理科学与运营方向（the Management Science and <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/运营管理' target='_blank'>Operations</a> Pathway）</li>	<li>战略与领导方向（Strategy and Leadership pathway）*(4)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQuFhk5gAriYXCCCCCCY3GxzVU9tILfKsKs_2jMpPzw6MwdHnymbhomW9KnfLlWB8n2O6bu9o' target='_blank'>Courses for 2015&ndash;16</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhf5wfFe86vu444444NyWqQeKE6xLTYoYoMEugshe-1y-2IGBzAmszaWy7FR_VbGuk7fsxpfqsa9ZTQ0CIjrjSnPjUM-YoclDeKN6ig0JReSCYJSh' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTHDkbcX2tIeDDDDD66yImrY_M6VOoetetiAPqQR152A5958kfE4DfncJq12zkGwefUlZsBlG2qu-hn6BRtKcUTecXd6h1RGBToed7pfMoCrPgQOVRezu' target='_blank'>Academic requirements - China</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=hrfXwi0Twdft_3ZyJJJJJJABFYZBVdWEDRQ-Q-o3OlqbUTA9TsSuYw_l5wNXbnxBFjrXdmg2Mb82KrzEDQvx4P0m3DM73k_2yXa5jQW3' target='_blank'>Requirements for Graduate Studies</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4eAkawhomDkaLeNQBmhkIBMbQ3RfA-jQgmrmSAbPA_huRIre0QuT3UiDJZtBEkmNespAAFzYqUqYT5jHPbvWju8I5RT_LeVy8r_x666VDlOR_vv0qZwqU6Dt' target='_blank'>MSc Management</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oEDkbcX29yHSSSSSEpImrY_M6VqQ8Q8BpwIsxTzgAb5T-nET-NED-aYT6pCV-j3KcNFKOIXfOJabckQ4-kMUFAhYbc3kPz3xWghY0zTf4chYRz48PchqJD4VbDTepmYnOkanbOE8vIur' target='_blank'>MSc Management Entry Requirements</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=-rGz4OsawJr7tUKgyiuoMRBZnyqp334dS43XjrrxF5qysE53TdS5sd-SwUd35yUrtLXhytIx3Kh4zI6GfGGTzdZCzR6E0OzYaHKS0rhFnZkMQwy6O1qeB5PpUO1FILQv_dzDR_fSPrAOowIO5ZpGhy