的初步认可，此为申请的前提及关键所在。需要<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/面试' target='_blank'>面试</a>，面试一般由导师举行，需要撰写<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/个人陈述' target='_blank'>个人陈述</a>。该项目并无明确的<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>提供给非欧盟国际学生，具体奖学金及申请方法等请见研究生的申请说明*(7)(8)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>帝国理工商学院PhD项目主要开设有以下四个研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/金融' target='_blank'>金融</a>（<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/金融' target='_blank'>Finance</a>）</li>	<li>医疗管理（Healthcare <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/管理学' target='_blank'>Management</a>）</li>	<li>组织与管理（Organisation And Management）</li>	<li>创新与企业管理（Innovation And <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/创业管理' target='_blank'>Entrepreneurship</a>）*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Trq48pWfw5T1UpRg333333Cx5Tsj9M0DEyEyh_q6N2ajXbm-TPs-BZsrXZRg40WLpURzdZb' target='_blank'>Courses for 2015&ndash;16</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Gr-dDkhIkJVBToBSwp-jqu_NhrJX41rC-EqWLv_4RH-SqWAGF__uTVWAJc3rMIc6JUh3Pc75-FbO36b7sDJiz_OFTW6b7e3jRp_TuRVPi0DpSEaD_DeUErlJ53PMg' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZi1LSONzHIbWWWWWcc03C14IO8GJgJgFN6Qucy4KyqQbNqpFNA0Fsfg3kXvrstTFsq43cEvr2KfwSeCjSpzAQsr42DB8i453HeEwQCJ3fkC' target='_blank'>Academic requirements - China</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=grPZ_xIkLbTirsKcddddddkOBX8cLVIWXc9C9CwJVl5fPH_WHBw7xAbyXA_VfaUTQsH3eHiA7oUAf_l5G_nOPQ3gky0tk3GeSuQlP4v3' target='_blank'>Requirements for Graduate Studies</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFTEwgqXDKdznRRagmdg3ClzFpyh6Gvbj9HVfDgEWTQKqhOVp3jXR2z1DKcrvmXOhXbWJSLQzm4zV-v05dj5VIdgnx1sW4RmJK7BoN2BsCQWfyU2b1_jsFpBXKr82AFKdG' target='_blank'>When to apply</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(5) 