拥有理科（Science）专业背景，无需工作经验。*(5)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Rr0CBrMNLT8196tlQCy40_hX9Jt_hUD-ERIEI13rSmTVQx5aMqpmuH9eILqpZ1B1OeOwMHjOfiivSSyyhm5S' target='_blank'>Courses for 2015&ndash;16</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7Pfkdft_3UzPPPPPPWpLXhlvPj4QSyryrb3lEm0y9GK95MpqodBTo85ADxBhoLTj6gkIjdku5-oYPgzxDkYvIQzv2Hsly02L8W_PNT1Cw_BGFmuB' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIezt2wLMS38_NLiiiii--APQWw3sgy_T_TcI7GN-BwkBUGLIUxcInAcSvTPu5dqS0RcSUwPN-rdqScRN4nANoBGzuDTPYgwFTUx645Rzn7xcZ' target='_blank'>Academic requirements - China</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6BGkNYOnRml______AFyvZmTDgu1Y1YkHhEs8CngNnD5WXDktXMut-q4Me3XAW-4gMu4AkLipW-4uM8HS58yK0YjXaLlt' target='_blank'>Requirements for Graduate Studies</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=vrJH6YySwHR2VfqHoooootPw-fFV2JYw4Q0b0b6FmNxRWDHkDnbTPs-BZsrkec6fh_ITx8rXEuJXvsa9ZTQ0CX5t6XefYgeCGcOKAmnULoDPp4-9_Wn7qQYVNfN61p' target='_blank'>When to apply</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_20wI0GioE3luQtuZhykRgyLq9B84ySGQf2f4NNvgVtLzc0UBf-B6OjEZWOpu4OH0faQ4jZfsZfczVpnfgKVS64TTFB7YF_PjJBAQJTxML1h5peQSuigdGuHH5KnTBqQnhzc' target='_blank'>MRes in Experimental Neuroscience</a> College London</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nHCFk2CbM-QS0SjQ1sRgyXeuNu1_T7WNQt1amETr2iM10RD0wYVmPFY6CYduDVQRi0HaCyJJRo3A57y9zUeD70_i4lUUhIUOnIl_DEpKN6D03V6BaDS7NRlZSbVmjAPNdCjrDh2_-7V' target='_blank'>Pre-sessional English Programme Entry Requirements</a> Imperial College London</p><h3>免疫学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td st