Energy Futures）项目设于生命科学系下，为期1年，属授课型项目。要求申请者本科毕业，二类A等荣誉学士学位或其同等水准以上学历，拥有<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/物理' target='_blank'>物理</a>科学或工程学等相关专业背景，无需工作经验。该项目的主要目标是培养未来能源部门的管理者，所学习的内容包括全球能源问题（Global Energy Issues）、可持续能源技术及二者与经济、环境、政策等的相互作用及影响。该项目不去分专业方向，无需撰写毕业论文，但需要完成一个研究项目*(5)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=srULj0RkkniNSQoT222222NZ5uSJofRO9E9EHM81U4CJcCp1TMpdH6DpiCn0BQ1IEiRHYgbC' target='_blank'>Courses for 2015&ndash;16</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23q9kltmgoxpKKKKKKXQN1ZvQ8najZq7q7dbLBiYfPLuPceuIhGgBhLVbaRxPZfFXcKTSUhTVFDwa1tFErKtT3u9T1AA0YjXaLlt25zLIZxecWv8D' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=vrJH6YhMLwBRm6ulfffffttGSTurogQx8Sc3c3qGdw705kN-kbMnWMDPvMQpZi7LBMO9KC62zl0279Qkb31PHRGVePhSeR3JR1mkvDhfECgAPs9j2NRzn7xcZ' target='_blank'>Academic requirements - China</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ErbpefwSL1wLXKbI2222221t3ipJ5W8rS8K1K1ZpsjPTS9r890PjTkEMLkt87q053BCb3fEO-glOr7irn6Q7pAITuBA0uPys8426WVO1' target='_blank'>Requirements for Graduate Studies</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Lr8sWSL2L4yTxY6tjjjjjzmGSTurogQx3QH8H8luYBknHN30NlHbC5hYy51Qh_y6VRevaETdDMVdR7irn6Q7p2w7fN3MVq3OrxQygX6WiOT8YqH5u3Cl0rBIF98DWH' target='_blank'>When to apply</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=frh1ZEifw5T1USJFZZZZZMWZVOBqiQKp261j1jCYvuSYjBGQBqQom1W8z1izhQnT7U6JLJaKScMKpql27OqMfs1M_l3cqsetLYJmOKyfrzrXIMHAF7MFBtM7Gaw7bSZ2d3SXl2vmFjrn6iIhu' target='_blank'>MSc in Sustainable Energy Futures</a> College London</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=qrTydPtcw1hiqHIBwwwwwIFKteC3p_jNV0V0r7oKLa1H6cdmL1omL7o0LgXoU28HvZrEb2AEv2CceZ9Bb7xY5RrBvT8Bb2xy