5分。该均分与国内学校质量直接相关，多在80-90分之间浮动，具体需视学校给的Conditional offer定。PhD项目则一般要求申请者硕士毕业，本科和硕士阶段的均分均不低于80分*(2)(3)</p><p>（4）该项目只接受秋季入学申请，实行滚动录取模式，一般11月下旬开始开放申请*(4)</p><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>帝国理工学院应用生物科学与生物技术硕士（MSc in Applied Biosciences and Biotechnology）项目设于生命科学系下，为期1年，属授课型项目。要求申请者本科毕业，二类A等荣誉学士学位或其同等水准以上学历，拥有<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/生物化学' target='_blank'>生物化学</a>或生物学等相关专业背景，无需工作经验。*(5)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=xrVOpg_nkkP-GMHy000000eYqg1yVeKbaNYAYAVw0WyiOpjPpCaIRwZ_VwzSTKIM-GteqLbNodcs' target='_blank'>Courses for 2015&ndash;16</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nVFL6UOjEcKssssssJovmOHfTUX0nrnrKaGpwkmXBmjpYajLKa3IK8OrWK3JC62zl027WEAYC620lP18ePra4g3_LEKblgoZ4tajecQ' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzAELAtGuFsvcccccCCyVeFbmN1wKfMfMXAF705kN-kb7xAbyXAUbReVy-YESBuVTteVNdY8kBuVetrvbR-1vXm9aAUfGqDkUQFy50Y9AIQb7s' target='_blank'>Academic requirements - China</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=7r_i3IKvwlsJdZWLSSSSSSpjPX5lRsDIpUPOPOucTw0yxZ2dZB4LhFi_6FExRJX7GoBI3_JceWVcUm_CStdReHrjOAbGO5qoQ-hILx8X' target='_blank'>Requirements for Graduate Studies</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aGRYwPxI162U22222RkuQ4Ewiz361j1jCYvyGROwqOgyUYg9CY8uCdmjQaKnpdlPCdg1g7kEFNitd2gfc0ZfDqkId78AcRf7iFHpzF_p7QwXWh8v' target='_blank'>When to apply</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZwnwmHu4cXL3XVSbld7UW5gtLydbWqnAaC2dlIH_vnEA1TbfpIR4_zeWDHN5sldb3Ogvjm-foTR2vMcPdb9smXTOlfZkW-UDOBhXSHAeI4MzbIOyNXWYOTq-hu_x9BiSEcTI65OcTXg' target='_blank'>MSc in Applied Biosciences and Biotechnology</a> College London</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?co