try）</li>	<li>生物结构与功能（Biological structure and function）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/生物物理' target='_blank'>生物物理</a>（Biophysics）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/细胞生物学' target='_blank'>细胞与分子生物学</a>，含神经科学（Cell and molecular biology, including neurosciences）</li>	<li>分子微生物学与感染（Molecular microbiology and infection）</li>	<li>结构生物学（Structural biology）</li>	<li>糖生物学（Glycobiology）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/免疫学' target='_blank'>免疫学</a>（Immunology）</li>	<li>分子生物科学（Molecular biosciences）</li>	<li>植物与微生物学（Plant and microbial sciences）*(5)</li></ul><p>结构分子生物学研究硕士的研究项目包括：</p><ul>	<li>大分子结构功能与结构生物信息学（Macromolecular structure function and structural bioinformatics）</li>	<li>X射线晶体学（X-ray crystallography）</li>	<li>生物核磁共振光谱学（Biological nuclear magnetic resonance spectroscopy）</li>	<li>低温电子显微镜（Cryo-electron microscopy）</li>	<li>质谱分析（Mass spectrometry）*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生项目列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJR6lwvLQzlrfYYYYYYWGEi7zKg_8rMrMPBFZODqzeqtZfBtRPBbGML_4rayswo_d1LE' target='_blank'>Courses for 2015&ndash;16</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6BAkawhoBzUTTTTTTO5Ao7I-H5GlDU9U9-_Q4-zoQuRQmQqh3OVb3ketBlNv4FSP-vyzNEyLwIF3RO1gJTBK0tSKZDh6F185UKhZfBrS2tg-Vbie' target='_blank'>English language requirement</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqV85wfFe8hGn-----E88nr-2UyfBdRgRgwLscv8FUJFVclLV6wL4nwhNgreZ5GhxzwhVUrd5umg28bVp7fVxW1jPNTGde4e6qJzw4UO7V9zGa' target='_blank'>Academic requirements - China</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTHik0k8m4zUTTTTTTDkv3HrKG1tZcZcgRiF4MXrVX-FUR-mgRakg0fcvxNp50Pyg0-rvMBpCpU64GSsBG0otjkC3-_O' target='_blank'>Requirements for Graduate Studies</a> Imperial College London</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHNWukXSVbGlmdddddntzkv3HrKG1X2CuCuh8rmEsSOm